Package: cscore
Type: Package
Title: Weighted Composite Scoring for Scales
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Hohjin", "Im", email = "hohjini@uci.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Weighted composite scoring for scales used in psychological and
    social behavioral research. Supports a variety of weighting schemes
    (average, correlation, regression, SD, mutual information, median, IRT,
    and PCA/GLM discriminant), returns composite reliability and convergent
    validity metrics, and integrates with DAG-based structural models for
    higher-order composites.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/imh-ds/cscore
BugReports: https://github.com/imh-ds/cscore/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
